---
// Ultra-compact About section for fast transactional container sales
---

<section class="py-8 bg-brand-black">
  <div class="content-wrap">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Company Info -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">
          LC Containers, LLC
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 text-ink-muted">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            Since 2003, LC Containers, LLC has been a trusted provider of high-quality shipping containers across Texas and beyond. With over two decades of experience, we specialize in offering both new and used containers for lease or purchase, tailored to meet the needs of businesses, contractors, and individuals alike.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            Conveniently located in Hutchins, Texas, just minutes from major highways and intermodal hubs, our team is dedicated to delivering reliable service, competitive pricing, and fast turnaround times. Whether you need a single container for personal storage or a fleet for commercial use, we're here to help you find the right solution.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            At LC Containers, LLC, our mission is simple: to provide dependable, affordable containers backed by honest service and real expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quick Contact -->
        <div class="mt-6 glass-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-3">Contact Information</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-red mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-ink-muted text-sm">info@lccontainer.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-red mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-ink-muted font-semibold text-sm">214-524-4168</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-red mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-ink-muted text-sm">Hutchins, Texas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right: Service Features -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">Customer Services</h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="glass-card p-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-brand-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h4a2 2 0 002-2V5z" />
